                <mxCell id="legend" value="&lt;b&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;LEGEND&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Topology (extends Lab 01)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;AS 65001 (R1/R2) &#8596; AS 65002 (R3) &#8596; AS 65003 (R4)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;R4 + PC2 + R3&#8596;R4 link are NEW&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;BGP Sessions&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;iBGP R1&#8596;R2 on Lo0 (OSPFv2/v3 carries Lo0)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;eBGP R1&#8596;R3 on 10.0.13.0/30 (v4+v6)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;eBGP R2&#8596;R3 on 10.0.23.0/30 (v4+v6)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;eBGP R3&#8596;R4 on 10.0.34.0/30 (v4+v6) NEW&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Link Types&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;White (w=2) &#8212; Routed P2P (/30)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;White (w=1) &#8212; Access port / LAN&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;White dashed &#8212; Logical loopback attach&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;AS Zones&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Teal dashed &#8212; AS 65001 (Enterprise)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Amber dashed &#8212; AS 65002 (ISP / Transit)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Violet dashed &#8212; AS 65003 (Remote Branch)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Interface Notation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;.N = IPv4 last octet (white)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;::N = IPv6 last hextet (cyan)&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Each octet hugs its own device (relative 0.08/0.92)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;BGP Best-Path Focus (Lab 02)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Two paths from AS 65001 to AS 65003 prefixes:&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;R1 &#8594; R3 &#8594; R4  and  R2 &#8594; R3 &#8594; R4&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Manipulate Weight / LOCAL_PREF / AS_PATH / MED / Origin&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;Dual-stack: best-path runs per AF independently" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#000000;strokeColor=#FFFFFF;fontColor=#FFFFFF;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=8;arcSize=3;" parent="1" vertex="1">
